description: Mandatory build/test/lint/e2e verification for code changes
alwaysApply: true
---

# Verification

After any code change (not asset-only), run and fix until green:

```bash
npm run build
npm run test
npm run lint
npm run test:e2e
```

Asset-only diffs (JPG/PNG under content package `assets/` / synced `public/`, no logic/UI behavior) may skip `test:e2e`; still run `build`/`lint` if TS registration changed.

Always use `npm run test:e2e` (never bare Playwright). E2e ports are `:5174` / `:3002`, not `:5173` / `:3001`.

Do not commit/push/PR unless the user asks.
